Name:           perl-Test-Class
Version:        0.52
Release:        12%{?dist}
Summary:        Easily create test classes in an xUnit/JUnit style
License:        GPL-1.0-or-later OR Artistic-1.0-Perl
URL:            https://metacpan.org/release/Test-Class
